    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="数学相关"><a href="#数学相关" class="headerlink" title="数学相关"></a>数学相关</h1><h2 id="取模的性质"><a href="#取模的性质" class="headerlink" title="取模的性质"></a>取模的性质</h2><p>$(a + b) \bmod p &#x3D; (a \bmod p + b \bmod p) \bmod p$</p><p>$(a - b) \bmod p &#x3D; (a \bmod p - b \bmod p) \bmod p$</p><p>$(a * b) \bmod p &#x3D; (a \bmod p * b \bmod p) \bmod p$</p><p>$a^b \bmod p &#x3D; (a \bmod p)^b \bmod p$</p><blockquote><p>[!WARNING]</p><p>除法没有相关性质，因此下面引入费马小定理与乘法逆元</p></blockquote><blockquote><p>若 $p$ 为素数，对于任何整数a，$a^p \equiv a \pmod{p}$</p></blockquote><p>为方便在取模意义下计算除法，为此引入乘法逆元：</p><blockquote><p>若 $b$ 是 $a$ 在模$p$意义下的乘法逆元，那么$ ab \equiv 1 \pmod{p} $</p></blockquote><p>那么</p><p>$ (x \div a) \bmod p &#x3D; (x * b) \bmod p$ </p><p>因此可应用乘法性质</p><p>由费马小定理易得 ：  $a$ 在模 $p$ 意义下的乘法逆元为 $a^{p-2}$ （p为素数）</p><p>一般计算逆元可用快速幂</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c++"><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">inline</span> ll <span class="hljs-title">binpow</span><span class="hljs-params">(ll a, ll b)</span></span>&#123;<br>    a %= mod; ll res = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span>(b)&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(b &amp; <span class="hljs-number">1</span>)   res = res * a % mod;<br>        a = a * a % mod;<br>        b &gt;&gt;= <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> res;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>一些情况可能会用到线性求 1-n 的逆元或先星球 1-n 阶乘的逆元</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c++"><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">inline</span> <span class="hljs-title">void</span><span class="hljs-params">(ll n)</span></span>&#123;<br>    inv[<span class="hljs-number">1</span>] = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">2</span>; i &lt;= n; i++)&#123;<br>        inv[i] = (ll)(p - p / i) * inv[p % i] % p;<br>    &#125;<span class="hljs-comment">//使用p - p/i防止出现负数</span><br>&#125;<span class="hljs-comment">//线性求逆元</span><br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">inline</span> <span class="hljs-title">void</span><span class="hljs-params">(ll n)</span></span>&#123;<br>    inv[n]=<span class="hljs-built_in">binpow</span>(fac[n],mod<span class="hljs-number">-2</span>);<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=n<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>;i&gt;=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;i--)&#123;<br>        inv[i]=inv[i<span class="hljs-number">+1</span>]*(i<span class="hljs-number">+1</span>)%mod;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<span class="hljs-comment">//线性求1-n阶乘逆元</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    
